data.description: This charming Metairie home is ready for your personal touches!  The front entry opens onto the living, dining and kitchen area for entertaining. The house is currently a 3-bedroom 2 bathroom but can easily be converted back to a 4 bedroom. The outdoor living space you'll enjoy a covered patio area with views of a custom fountain feature. Plenty of storage space in the outdoor shed.
